=== Phase 1:
üó≥[üí∞] ‚Üî üöøü•óüõè  Users vote-with-money to buy future Goods and Services.
üó≥[üìÉ‚úçüë∑] ‚Üî üöøü•óüõè & üèûüõ†  Users vote-with-future-work to buy future Goods and Services and also receive access to the Land and Tools required for that production.
