üìÉ‚úÖ: üèûüõ† ‚áâ üë∑  Land and Tools ownership vests as work is completed.
üèû + üõ† + üë∑ ‚áâ üöøü•óüõè ‚áâ üë∑  When you own Land, Tools and Work, you own those future Goods and Services without purchase.
üìÉ‚úçüë∑ ‚Üî üìÉ‚úçüë∑  When you buy future Goods and Services with future Work, you implicitly trade future Work with others, and so create a true insurance network.

